{"tid":248874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳日君斥教廷為與中國建交：不惜付出任何代價","createTime":"2017-05-19T01:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T09:29:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8efe2246f4678896b3c2b7832d09eb1178c3e974","tid":248874,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495157956_5fa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495157956_5fa0.jpg&h=5a95a42b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君最近接受英國天主教雜誌Catholic Herald專訪時，批評教廷為與中國建交，「不惜付出任何代價」，過程中未有聆聽他及其他中國神職人員的意見。他認為教會不應向任何地上的政府叩頭，只有教會能夠堅持立場，勿輕言讓步，才能達至成果。<br />\n<br />\n他相信中梵雙方的協議已準備就緒，但至今仍未簽定，相信是中國政府要求教廷交出所有權力，包括主教任命權及其他控制教會的權力，陳指這是教會不可能接受，所以政府至今拒絕簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713382&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713382%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fa6af01b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713382%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=51141aee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713382&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a>"},{"pid":"fcc8828b0856005da62952134ee2a83c48f241d2","tid":248874,"uid":110271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"為了錢賣了主"},{"pid":"2f43dd54ff6367c302515c37b91a60f0d0574f7c","tid":248874,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"on9,無讀過天主教既歷史呀,呢個係佢地一向作風呀"},{"pid":"7930dff8b34c19cba3b692